  "description": "Gorenje's freestanding side-by-side refrigerator is an appliance for a spacious kitchen and a fairly large family. As for its class of devices, the model can be attributed to the solutions of the initial price segment. But despite this, there are two cooling circuits for flexible temperature settings (an internal touch panel is proposed for control), and there is also a reliable inverter compressor. The inverter, among other things, has a positive effect on energy consumption (it winds 289 kWh on the meter per year, which corresponds to class E (analogue of A ++)). Refrigerator Gorenje NRS 8182 KX received a 171-liter freezer, which is located on the left. Its useful space is divided into 6 zones (4 open shelves and 2 drawers), plus there are four door baskets. The 266-liter refrigerating chamber has a similar organization, only there is one less shelf on the doors (and the increased width of the compartment actually provides a gain in volume). During the day, the model is able to freeze up to 10 kg of food, and the cold in case of problems with light should remain inside for about 10 hours. Other features of the device include the Full No Frost system, the presence of not only quick freezing and cooling, but also a vacation mode, as well as a moderate noise level (up to 42 dB).",
